name: Ur'Ru'r (V)
Lore: 'Fierce Tusken Raider. Ransacks homes and moisture farms on the borders of Mos Espa.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. During your deploy phase, if with URoRRuR''R''R, may deploy a weapon with ''Tusken'' in lore here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle; your weapon destiny draws for such weapons are +2. During your deploy phase, may move Ur''Ru''r as a regular move.',
